Subject: [PATCH v32 4/6] ARM: dts: n900: Add reg property to the LP5523 channel node
Date:   Wed, 22 Jul 2020 10:31:44 -0500
Message-ID: <20200722153146.8767-5-dmurphy@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.27.0
In-Reply-To: <20200722153146.8767-1-dmurphy@ti.com>
